name: 杰西卡·兰道
introduction: Jessica Landaw is an American director, editor and producer of film and television.Jessica LandawOccupationFilm director, film editor, television director, television editor, television producerYears active1994–presentShe has directed a number of documentaries and short films in career as well as working as an editor on the films Mighty Morphin Power Rangers: The Movie (1995), The Great White Hype (1996), The War at Home (1996) and The House of Yes (1997).[1]As a television director her credits are Judging Amy, Cold Case, Bones, One Tree Hill and web series The Booth at the End starring Xander Berkeley.[2]
